   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=811.topic>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_cry.gif" align=absmiddle>  57 Earth? what's wrong with that one?</span><hr size=1> Ok, I'm not a fast-leveler really. So I finally dinged 57 yesterday and was pretty happy.<br>
Now..I knew that SoS wouldnt help me much because of my spec in Evocation.<br>
But I was really looking forward to the new Pet.<br>
I was hunting at the plateau in SD and used Voc air so far (+Plate armor+Muzzle plus sometimes some proc weapons)<br>
<br>
So after ding I brought up GVoc earth (+Plate armor +Muzzle), hoping to be able to fight a bit faster now.<br>
<br>
Pulled one...I couldnt believe how fast the HPs of the pet went down. I had to chainnuke just to prevent it from dieing. Pet survived with 10% HPs.<br>
<br>
tried it again...this time it ended up with 4% exp.<br>
<br>
Now the fights were much faster, but I had to nuke like crazy, so thats very ineffective.<br>
<br>
sorry, I cant really describe here *how* shocked I was about the speed GVoc earth lost all of its HPs.<br>
<br>
Based on that experience I cannot imagine any solo fight where GVoc earth would do any good. <br>
<br>
Is it really that bad as it seems and am I really stuck until lvl 59 for some *real* improvements? :-( <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=downburstthemage>downburstthemage</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 8<br> <font color=#333333>(11/7/02 3:52 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=811.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_cry.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: 57 Earth? what's wrong with that one?</span><hr size=1> Normally 57 earth pet is used for chaincasting (of course for those under 60 and with no epic) and they do a pretty decent job at it. Yes they get hit a lot but make it up with there higher hp which grants you more time to med let it get down to 20 (sometimes lower if you re really sure about the atacks the mob is making) and start casting a new one, /pet get lost when summon is almost done and you re new reinforcement has arrived.<br>
<br>
Now you can decide to give it a DS and / or burnout xx and let it fight again and keep repeating this till mobis dead.<br>
<br>
Try chaincasting with other pets, they just go down faster and thus is more mana expensive, in my eyes this is what the 57 earth pet is all about.<br>
<br>
Downburst Stardestroyer<br>
Archmage of &lt;&lt;==Halcyon Conclave==&gt;&gt;<br>
 <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.halcyonconclave.com/images/db1.jpg"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><!--EZCODE HR START--><hr /><!--EZCODE HR END--><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.halcyonconclave.com"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.halcyonconclave.com/images/minihc.gif"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--> <br>
<br>
<br>
  </p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=zyphyr>Zyphyr</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Sage</span><br>  Posts: 656<br> <font color=#333333>(11/8/02 12:46 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=811.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_cry.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: 57 Earth? what's wrong with that one?</span><hr size=1> GVoC:Earth has a low AC. Every Earth pet has that problem. Surely you haven't forgotten that already. <p><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="font-size:medium;">Zyphyr Runnersbane</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--><br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://&quot;http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=44185&quot;">Vending Machine and Disciple of Zomm</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
