<br>
I've used chaincasting since I first had a mage, back before Kunark, so the technique isn't new to me.  Once you have the timing down, it's very rare that anything odd will happen.  About the only thing I can think of is an add at the wrong time, or having my pet die too soon.<br>
<br>
Oh, and fizzles.  God, I hate fizzles.<br>
<br>
But past that, it's pretty safe.<br>
<br>
